<!--[/!\ DEPRECATED ]*********************************
This service allow to create new customer
  Potential errors :
    * [S-002] [HTTP-409_functional]  User already exists, please choose another login to create a newer customer
    * [S-003] [HTTP-0_technical]  can't connect to database
    * [ERR-0000] [HTTP-500_technical]  undefine error occurs
    * [ERR-003] [HTTP-500_technical]  Preference key is require
-->
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:ns="http://inugami.io">"
	<soapenv:Header/>
	<soapenv:Body>
		<ns:createUser>
          <user>
            <id>Long</id>
            <firstName>String</firstName>
            <lastName>String</lastName>
            <email>String</email>
            <roles>String</roles>
            <globalPreference>
              <consents>
                <newsletter>boolean</newsletter>
                <email>boolean</email>
                <phone>boolean</phone>
              </consents>
              <!--multiple occurrence possible-->
              <preferences>
                <!--key is mandatory
                  Potential errors :
                    * [ERR-003] [HTTP-500_technical]  Preference key is require
                -->
                <key>String</key>
                <value>String</value>
                <!--multiple occurrence possible-->
                <histories>
                  <date>Calendar</date>
                  <user>String</user>
                  <!--multiple occurrence possible-->
                  <tags>
                    <name>String</name>
                    <level>int</level>
                  </tags>
                </histories>
              </preferences>
            </globalPreference>
          </user>
		</ns:createUser>
	</soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
